metadata.name: I was born like this 15
metadata.description:
1:1 piece from upcoming genesis collection of Mutant Chicks Unchained. This is tribute to Avril15.eth. 

Her name is Avril and she is mutant. She barks out loud. If u hang out for too long with her, she'll brainwash u into believing in yourself & becoming unchained and making your mark upon the metaverse #stayweird
